    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid & Dependable \u2013 A Well-Maintained Ride Ready for the Road! \ud83d\ude97\n\nIf you're in the market for a reliable everyday vehicle, this one is worth a serious look! This car is in good condition \u2014 it's been well cared for and shows it. You'll find it drives smoothly and comfortably, making it a great fit for commutes, errands, or weekend adventures. There are minor signs of normal wear consistent with its age, but nothing that affects performance or reliability. A trustworthy vehicle at a fair, honest price \u2014 come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "A solid opportunity to get behind the wheel of a functional, road-ready vehicle at a great value price! This car does its job reliably day-to-day, though it does show its age \u2014 you'll notice some visible wear on the exterior, and the interior reflects years of use. There are a few mechanical items that may benefit from attention down the road, so we've priced it accordingly. If you're looking for honest, practical transportation without the premium price tag, this could be a great fit!",
      "price": 22000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a fair-condition car suitable for reliable everyday transportation. The exterior shows visible wear, including minor dents, light scratches, and some areas where the paint has faded or chipped. There may be small surface rust spots in a few locations, though nothing structurally compromising. The interior is functional but shows signs of use \u2014 expect worn upholstery, some scuffs on trim panels, and general aging consistent with a well-used vehicle. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but prospective buyers should anticipate that some components may need attention in the near term, such as worn belts, aging fluids, or minor suspension wear. We recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting. This is a solid choice for a budget-conscious buyer who wants dependable transportation and doesn't mind putting in a little work to bring it up to their standards.",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, and we want to be fully transparent about its current state. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 numerous scratches, several dents, and areas where the paint has faded, chipped, or peeled. The body may have some rust present. The interior is heavily worn with torn or damaged upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and a general sense of long, hard use. Mechanically, this car runs and drives, but it has known issues that will require attention \u2014 expect to invest in repairs to bring it to a reliable standard. It is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs basic transportation and is comfortable with its limitations. This is not a worry-free daily driver, and we strongly encourage a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're taking on. Priced accordingly to reflect its condition honestly.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in genuinely mint condition \u2014 a designation we do not use lightly. The exterior is immaculate, with original factory paint retaining its full depth and luster, completely free of scratches, dents, chips, or any blemishes whatsoever. Panel gaps are uniform and precise, and all trim pieces, moldings, and glass are in perfect order. The interior is equally impressive, showing no wear on the seats, carpets, headliner, or dashboard \u2014 it presents as though it just left the showroom floor. All electronics, controls, and features function exactly as intended, with no warning lights or quirks to report. Under the hood, the engine is clean and well-maintained, with full service records available for your review. Mechanically, the vehicle drives with confidence \u2014 smooth, responsive, and tight, with no unusual noises, vibrations, or hesitations. Tires have excellent tread remaining and wear evenly. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that has been exceptionally cared for throughout its life. Ideal for a buyer who wants a truly turn-key vehicle with no surprises.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Attention project car lovers and hands-on mechanics \u2014 here's your next rewarding build! This vehicle is being sold as-is in poor condition, which means it comes with notable mechanical issues and visible wear throughout. It's not a daily driver in its current state, but with the right skills and some elbow grease, there's real potential here. If you love a challenge and enjoy bringing a car back to life, this could be exactly what you've been searching for \u2014 priced to reflect its current condition and ready for its next chapter!",
      "price": 4000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
